org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface INumericLiteralNode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NumericLiteralNode

    public interface INumericLiteralNode
    An AST node representing a numeric literal such as 3, 0x1FFF, or -1.23e10.

    This node has no children.
